OL,3,CRepairs promised for century-old man-
OL,4,Cmade lake
OL,6,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister is
OL,7,Fpromising to make improvements to the
OL,8,Fwall around a bathing pool in St
OL,9,FAubins Bay.
OL,11,FThe Victoria Marine Lake has been a
OL,12,Fstaple of the bay for over a century
OL,13,Fbut has deteriorated to such an extent
OL,14,Fthat the wall has started to cave in.
OL,16,FIn January 2024, the Parish of St
OL,17,FHelier could not prioritise funds to
OL,18,Frepair and operate the pool, despite
OL,19,Facknowledging its heritage.
