OL,3,CRepairs promised for century-old man-
OL,4,Cmade lake
OL,6,FHowever, Connetable Andy Jehan says
OL,7,Fthat repairs could take place in 2025.
OL,9,FHe explains: "We looked at it early
OL,10,Flast year. The Connetable of St Helier
OL,11,Fand I were here with officers in
OL,12,FOctober.
OL,14,F"We are going to try and make it safe.
OL,15,FIn the longer term, there are plans
OL,16,Ffor a 50-metre pool with the
OL,17,FWaterfront.
OL,19,F"In the short-term, we'll be looking
OL,20,Fto make it safe this year."
