OL,3,CRepairs promised for century-old man-
OL,4,Cmade lake
OL,6,FThe Victoria Marine Lake was built in
OL,7,F1896 for the Queen's Diamond Jubilee.
OL,9,FThe wall was made to hold water to
OL,10,Fcreate a lido, making it the biggest
OL,11,Fof its kind in the British Isles at
OL,12,Fthe time.
OL,14,FIn 2014, around #314,000 was spent to
OL,15,Fundertake maintenance work.
OL,17,FJersey residents hope that repairs can
OL,18,Fhelp save the crumbling structure
OL,19,Fbefore further damage is caused.
